social_posts.post_text: Shoutout to @dickssportinggoods for hooking it up with the new gear. Check them out for the best kicks and apparel – they have everything you need whether you’re on the go, chilling after a game or getting some shots up. #DKSPartner

I am beyond grateful. Grateful to the city and organization that made a dream come true, to the people who supported us every step of the way, my coaches, teammates, family, and friends. My time in Phoenix was special, and the city and people will remain near and dear to my heart.

So an enormous thank you @suns and all those who made and will continue to make it go, top to bottom. I love you all and wish I could tell you one by one.

Broooooklynnnn, I am excited for this new adventure. LETS HOOP

ps - twins remain locked in 🤝

Less than 2 weeks out from the inaugural Rush to Crush Cancer bike ride!

This fundraiser for the UPMC Hillman Cancer Center is pretty dope and personal to myself and the fam, as my Uncle Tony is currently undergoing treatment for cancer

Tony and the family have created a team for the ride and I am excited to be a part of it! The fundraising effort is well underway, and we are blessed to continue to support Tony and all those who are battling cancer, those who care for our loved ones, and those who are working constantly to eradicate the disease

The link to donate is in my bio, everything and anything is appreciated ❤️
